### Authentication

### Login with email
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kemokingo44@gmail.com",
  "password": "787898787899"
}

### Register as a regular user
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "confirm_password": "testpass123",
  "role": "user"
}

### Register as an academy user
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ahmedacademy",
  "email": "testacademy@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "confirm_password": "testpass123",
  "role": "academy"
}

### Register academy details
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/academy/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Email Test",
  "email": "kemokingo44@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "confirm_password": "testpass123",
  "academy_name": "Email Test Academy",
  "phone": "01012345678",
  "description": "Testing email system"
}

### Login as a regular user
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kemokingo44@gmail.com",
  "password": "kemo&24680"
}

### Login as an approved academy
### First approve the academy from Django admin, then try again
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kemokingo44@gmail.com",
  "password": "787898787899"
}

### Try to login as a pending academy
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "karimkfawzy44@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

### Refresh token
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "<REFRESH_TOKEN>"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/logout/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "<REFRESH_TOKEN>"
}

### Get current user info
GET http://localhost:8000/auth/me/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Validation examples

### Wrong confirm password
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser2",
  "email": "testuser2@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "confirm_password": "wrongpassword",
  "role": "user"
}

### Duplicate username
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "different@gmail.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "confirm_password": "testpass123",
  "role": "user"
}

### Bookings

### Create a booking
POST http://localhost:8000/bookings/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "course": 3,
  "trainer": 3,
  "scheduled_date": "2026-06-08",
  "start_time": "09:00",
  "notes": "I prefer morning sessions"
}

### Try to book the same trainer at the same date and time
POST http://localhost:8000/bookings/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "course": 3,
  "trainer": 7,
  "scheduled_date": "2026-04-28",
  "start_time": "10:00",
  "notes": "duplicate booking test"
}

### Try to book as an academy user
POST http://localhost:8000/bookings/create/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "course": 1,
  "trainer": 3,
  "scheduled_date": "2026-05-10",
  "start_time": "09:00"
}

### Get all my bookings
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Get booking detail
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/30/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Cancel a booking
PATCH http://localhost:8000/bookings/1/cancel/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Check available slots

### Working day
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/availability/?trainer=3&course=3&date=2026-05-02
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Non-working day
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/availability/?trainer=6&course=1&date=2026-04-24
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Past date
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/availability/?trainer=7&course=2&date=2026-04-28
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Missing params
GET http://localhost:8000/bookings/availability/?trainer=7&course=2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Dashboard - academy profile

### Get academy profile
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/profile/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Update academy profile
PATCH http://localhost:8000/dashboard/profile/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "motaz academy",
  "description": "We offer a wide range of courses in various fields including programming, design, marketing, and more. Our experienced instructors and comprehensive curriculum ensure that you gain the skills needed to succeed in your career."
}

### Add contact
POST http://localhost:8000/dashboard/profile/contacts/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "type": "phone",
  "value": "01012345678"
}

### Delete contact
DELETE http://localhost:8000/dashboard/profile/contacts/18/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Try accessing profile with a regular user token
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/profile/
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Dashboard - trainers

### Create a trainer
POST http://localhost:8000/dashboard/trainers/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "gender": "male",
  "bio": "Test bio",
  "car_model": "Honda Civic",
  "experience_years": 5,
  "working_days": ["monday", "sunday"],
  "session_start_time": "09:00",
  "session_end_time": "17:00",
  "is_active": true
}

### Update trainer
PATCH http://localhost:8000/dashboard/trainers/12/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "experience_years": 7
}

### Delete trainer
DELETE http://localhost:8000/dashboard/trainers/12/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Dashboard - courses

### Get all academy courses
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/courses/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Add new course
POST http://localhost:8000/dashboard/courses/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "New Manual Course",
  "description": "Learn manual driving",
  "price": "299.00",
  "sessions": 10,
  "duration": 60,
  "quantity": 20,
  "transmission": "manual",
  "is_active": true,
  "trainers": [14]
}

### Get course detail
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/courses/16/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Update course
PATCH http://localhost:8000/dashboard/courses/16/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "price": "350.00",
  "quantity": 25
}

### Delete course
DELETE http://localhost:8000/dashboard/courses/16/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Dashboard - bookings

### Get all academy bookings
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Filter bookings by status
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/?status=confirmed
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Filter bookings by trainer
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/?trainer=14
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Filter bookings by course
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/?course=17
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Get booking detail
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/2/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Update booking status to completed
PATCH http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/2/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Get academy booking stats
GET http://localhost:8000/dashboard/bookings/stats/
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Reviews

### Review an academy
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "content_type": "academy",
  "object_id": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "text": "Great academy, highly recommended!"
}

### Review a course
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "content_type": "course",
  "object_id": 1,
  "rating": 4,
  "text": "Very good course, learned a lot!"
}

### Review a trainer
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "content_type": "trainer",
  "object_id": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "text": "Amazing trainer, very patient!"
}

### Try to review the same object twice
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "content_type": "academy",
  "object_id": 1,
  "rating": 3,
  "text": "Trying to review again"
}

### Try to review without a token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/reviews/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content_type": "academy",
  "object_id": 1,
  "rating": 5,
  "text": "No token test"
}
